          <title>TikTok Loses Court Battle Over Foreign Ownership</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Federal appeals court rules against TikTok in a dispute over its foreign ownership and alleged ties to the Chinese government, denying the company's petition to overturn a law requiring it to divest US operations from its Chinese parent company.]]></description>
